# Bun Preferences

Always prefer Bun over Node.js/npm for all operations:

- Package manager: `bun install`, `bun add`, `bun remove` (not npm/yarn/pnpm)
- Running scripts: `bun run dev`, `bun run build` (not npm run)
- Executing packages: `bunx` (not npx)
- Running files: `bun script.ts` (not node/ts-node)

Examples:
```bash
# Installing dependencies
bun install

# Adding a package
bun add zod

# Running dev server
bun run dev

# Executing a one-off package
bunx convex dev
bunx shadcn@latest add button
```
